  "title": "Senior M&E Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Co-ordination\n     and supervision of M&E Works</li><li>Liaise\n     with M&E Consultants</li><li>Ascertain\n     and make provision for all M&E and building services in collaboration\n     with the project staff</li><li>Monitor\n     progress, quality of workmanship and compliance with authority\n     requirements</li><li>Highlight\n     and advise the project staff on the interfacing of M&E services and\n     the building works</li><li>Coordination\n     with multiple parties not limiting to design consultants / engineers,\n     clients' project representatives, statutory / authority agencies etc, for\n     the establishment of the design deliverables requirements for submission</li><li>Review\n     design deliverables together with the design consultants / engineers and\n     ensure that it is in order for submission</li><li>Attend\n     to technical clarifications as and when required to address technical\n     issues and establish method statements</li><li>Project\n     Management and sites supervision works</li><li>Able\n     to coordinate with contractors and consultants for engineering issues and\n     drawing plans</li><li>Perform\n     all duties in accordance with company policies, processes, systems and\n     procedures</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum\n     8 years engineering experience with Recognised Degree in relevant field,\n     and at least 5 years of supervision experience of Building Services work\n     in construction site for project of similar scale and complexity.</li></ul>",
